  "code": "stateDiagram\n  S1: INITIAL\n  S2: DOWNLOADING\n  S3: UNCONFIRMED\n  S4: REJECTED\n  S5: CONFIRMED\n\n  [*] --> S1\n  S1 --> S2: download profile\n  S2 --> S3: download complete\n  S2 --> S1: download error\n  S3 --> S4: user rejects\n  S3 --> S5: user confirms\n",
  "diagram_type": "size:200..250",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T03:23:20.251923",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户资料下载的状态流转图。从初始状态开始，用户触发下载后进入下载中状态，下载完成后需要用户确认，确认通过才算最终完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下：起点到初始状态，然后下载中，再到待确认，最后确认完成。那如果下载失败或者用户拒绝的情况需要处理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，下载出错要能回到初始状态让用户重试，用户拒绝的话要有个拒绝状态结束流程。所以中间加个待确认状态，从那里分叉到确认完成或拒绝。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：起点指向INITIAL，INITIAL通过download profile转到DOWNLOADING，DOWNLOADING通过download complete转到UNCONFIRMED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后UNCONFIRMED分两条线，user confirms到CONFIRMED，user rejects到REJECTED。别忘了DOWNLOADING还要有个返回INITIAL的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S2",
        "S1",
        "S3",
        "S5",
        "S4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了：DOWNLOADING在download error时回到INITIAL，UNCONFIRMED通过user confirms到CONFIRMED，通过user rejects到REJECTED。五个状态都齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S2",
        "S1",
        "S3",
        "S5",
        "S4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "状态名用英文大写对吧？INITIAL、DOWNLOADING、UNCONFIRMED、REJECTED、CONFIRMED。确认一下流转关系有没有遗漏。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查完毕，七条流转关系都正确：起点到INITIAL，下载前进后退，下载完成到待确认，最后确认或拒绝。状态命名也统一了。",
      "elements_involved": [
